<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>UDAAN – This is not a charity. This is a revolution.</title>

<!-- Google Fonts -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root {
    --bg: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1a1f4a 0%, #050716 70%);
    --gold: #D4AF37;
    --ivory: #F8F1E9;
    --soft: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    --glow: 0 0 40px rgba(212,175,55,0.6);
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ivory);
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
}

/* LOGO */
#logo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2rem;
    left: 2rem;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: var(--glow);
    z-index: 10;
}

@media(max-width:768px){
    #logo {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
    }
}

/* CURSOR */
.cursor {
    position: fixed;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--gold), transparent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    mix-blend-mode: difference;
}

/* PARTICLES */
#particles {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
}
.particle {
    position: absolute;
    width: 3px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.5;
    animation: float 25s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes float {
    from { transform: translateY(110vh); opacity:0; }
    to { transform: translateY(-120px); opacity:0; }
}

/* HERO */
#hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 2rem;
}

.hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 13vw, 9rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    text-shadow: var(--glow);
}

.hero-sub {
    max-width: 820px;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
}

.tagline {
    margin-top: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--gold);
}

/* BUTTON */
.cta {
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 3rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* SECTION */
section {
    padding: 8rem 10vw;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
}

.section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.section-text {
    max-width: 900px;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
}

/* CARDS */
.cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px,1fr));
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
}
.card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--soft);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.3);
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    opacity: 0.8;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<img src="logo.jpg" alt="Sange Education & Charitable Trust" id="logo">

<div class="cursor"></div>
<div id="particles"></div>

<div id="hero">
    <h1 class="hero-title">UDAAN</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
        This is not about donations.
        This is about <strong>dignity</strong>, <strong>power</strong>, and <strong>breaking the cycle forever</strong>.
    </p>
    <div class="tagline">THIS IS NOT A CHARITY · THIS IS A REVOLUTION</div>
    <button class="cta">JOIN THE MOVEMENT</button>
</div>

<section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Why UDAAN Exists</h2>
    <p class="section-text">
        Charity feeds hunger for a day.
        UDAAN destroys the system that creates hunger.
        We equip people to rise.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Our Manifesto</h2>
    <div class="cards">
        <div class="card"><h3>Education as Power</h3><p>Knowledge is a right.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Skill Before Sympathy</h3><p>We build capability.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Dignity First</h3><p>Strength over pity.</p></div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    © 2025 UDAAN Trust<br>
    Built to rise.
</footer>

<script>
const cursor = document.querySelector('.cursor');
document.addEventListener('mousemove', e => {
    cursor.style.left = e.clientX + 'px';
    cursor.style.top = e.clientY + 'px';
});

const container = document.getElementById('particles');
for(let i=0;i<60;i++){
    const p = document.createElement('div');
    p.className = 'particle';
    p.style.left = Math.random()*100 + '%';
    container.appendChild(p);
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
